By Andile Mngxitama There is a rapid mushrooming of Bill Gates’s agents and peddlers of 5G uncritically through pseudo science and even trying to mobilize African thinking systems to justify why we must accept a technology which has massive potentially harmful effects. These black crusaders for 5G don’t even want to hear anything about getting guarantees that we would be safe. What is the hurry for? We say NO to Bill Gates‘s vaccines and NO to 5G without guarantees that our health is not in danger. Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.